author: dcovucci@thedailydot.com (David Covucci)
title: Drudge Report Accidentally Includes Jar Jar Binks in Story on Iran Tthreat
text:
Wookiepedia | Remix by Jason Reed BTW 
Two years ago, a theory about Jar Jar Binks being the biggest evil mastermind in the entire Star Wars universe went viral, with the whole web awed by the possibility. 
It turned out to be (most likely) bunk, but what if it wasn’t a galaxy far, far away where the aggravating Gunga was pulling the strings behind the scene? What if it was— 
… GASP 
… DRUMROLL 
OUR UNIVERSE!!! 
That’s right. According to leading conservative rabble-rouser Matt Drudge, proprietor of Drudge Report , the Iranian missile test is spearheaded by Jar Jar. 
Well, at least according to the site’s photo for its article on the test.
